{"id":"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http","title":"瞭解使用 HTTP 與後端服務通訊","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1z3u8zvhhoar09xqua5gnqgus\">瞭解使用 HTTP 與後端服務通訊<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cyllngi7g8now7nyzf1erbj5s\">大多數前端應用都要透過 HTTP 協定與伺服器通訊，才能下載或上傳資料並訪問其它後端服務。Angular 給應用提供了一個 HTTP 用戶端 API，也就是 <code>@angular/common/<a href=\"api/common/http\" class=\"code-anchor\">http</a></code> 中的 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 服務類別。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1mcguuy84a1ltfk4ksodb8v1t\">在使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientModule</a></code> 之前，你應該對下列內容有基本的瞭解：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"78gqqpxnzs5bqi8d4zmijgaes\">TypeScript 程式設計</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d61exg56xvc01v8biqt4lzob5\">HTTP 協定的用法</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"29peedffjewxu5x1iry7bqfm6\">Angular 的應用設計基礎，就像<a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 基本概念</a>中描述的那樣</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1b72hf0merf2gcrnthuyuzp8v\">Observable 的技術和運算符。請參閱 <a href=\"guide/observables\">Observables 指南</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"http-client-service-features\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dubnzi6umb9w8yc39hzpifjgx\">HTTP 用戶端服務屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4qxc6hb42sgwwz0fzeak98140\">HTTP 用戶端服務提供了以下主要功能。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cnhvju4ojbomulycltcr0gjik\">請求<a href=\"guide/http-request-data-from-server\">型別化回應物件</a>的能力</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a9ilig81uj0vndbbk8fk7yztq\">通道式<a href=\"guide/http-handle-request-errors\">錯誤處理</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dzfwr8mgwnbocnhylooqjcqr9\"><a href=\"guide/http-test-requests\">可測試性</a>的屬性</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3c6ynycbh1su13xb64z2vgwlf\">對請求和回應的<a href=\"guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\">攔截</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"407r2fj2mi5kvg7imj9zdcpe\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4x4r50i8eetzljix1n1m0x61d\"><a href=\"guide/http-setup-server-communication\">伺服器通訊設定</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Wed Aug 16 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - guide/docs-style-guide\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/http-server-communication\n - guide/npm-packages\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/rx-library\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - start/start-data\n - tutorial/tour-of-heroes/toh-pt4\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - api/common/http/HttpClientModule\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/http-handle-request-errors\n - guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\n - guide/http-request-data-from-server\n - guide/http-setup-server-communication\n - guide/http-test-requests\n - guide/observables\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\n-->"}